for our tambourine base.

163
00:07:19.569 --> 00:07:21.988
Do you see two circles we could use?

164
00:07:23.906 --> 00:07:25.575
The paper plates.

165
00:07:28.035 --> 00:07:30.621
Paper plate delivery!

166
00:07:30.705 --> 00:07:32.039
Thanks. Pandy.

167
00:07:32.123 --> 00:07:35.626
