on top of each other. like this.

168
00:07:35.710 --> 00:07:37.837
and punch holes around the edges.

169
00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:39.922
I've got the hole puncher right here.

170
00:07:44.135 --> 00:07:47.221
Next. we need some bells
for that tambourine ring.

171
00:07:47.305 --> 00:07:48.431
I've got you.

172
00:07:50.433 --> 00:07:52.977
[bells jingling]

173
00:07:53.644 --> 00:07:54.604
Thanks. DJ.

174
00:07:54.687 --> 00:07:57.231
