we need to decorate it.

181
00:08:17.627 --> 00:08:20.296
Got to have a little sparkle
for my tambourine.

182
00:08:26.385 --> 00:08:29.013
Ta-da! Thanks so much for helping me.

183
00:08:29.096 --> 00:08:31.307
-You saved my whole show.
-[jingling]

184
00:08:31.390 --> 00:08:33.017
-[banjo strumming]
-Oh!

185
00:08:33.100 --> 00:08:35.770
Time to get shakin'. See you out there!

186
00:08:35.853 --> 00:08:37.396
