00:21:15.320 --> 00:21:17.781
I painted mine with some funky stripes.

486
00:21:17.864 --> 00:21:19.157
just like mine.

487
00:21:19.241 --> 00:21:20.867
<i>♪ Wiggly-wiggly-wig! ♪</i>

488
00:21:20.951 --> 00:21:22.202
Ha-ha-ha!

489
00:21:22.286 --> 00:21:26.832
Now we gotta close up one end
with this piece of felt and rubber band.

490
00:21:26.915 --> 00:21:29.710
-Now. here comes the funky part.
-[funky music playing]

491
00:21:29.793 --> 00:21:32.838
Whoa! This is some groovy foil! Ha-ha!

492
00:21:33.338 --> 00:21:36.675
Now we're gonna put these
inside our painted roll.

493
00:21:39.303 --> 00:21:41.847
You ready for
the secret musical ingredient?

494
00:21:42.597 --> 00:21:44.099
Sprinkles!

495
00:21:44.182 --> 00:21:48.895
These sprinkles
are gonna bring all the purrs. trust me.

496
00:21:49.479 --> 00:21:52.733
That's what I'm talking about.
Now close up the other end.

497
00:21:54.443 --> 00:21:59.406
And if you want to make it extra funky.
you can draw a kitty face on each end.

498
00:22:06.288 --> 00:22:07.956
Aw. yeah!

499
00:22:08.040 --> 00:22:09.875
Now we can purr together.

500
00:22:09.958 --> 00:22:12.169
-Purr!
-[rattling]

501
00:22:13.795 --> 00:22:15.797
[rattling]

502
00:22:17.799 --> 00:22:20.135
Happy Purrsday. y'all!

503
00:22:22.471 --> 00:22:25.807
These little cuties really put on
a great show. don't you think?

504
00:22:25.891 --> 00:22:28.226
And we can't forget about the CatRat.

505
00:22:28.310 --> 00:22:29.144
Ha-cha!

506
00:22:29.728 --> 00:22:32.022
And Floyd was definitely
getting in on the groove.

507
00:22:32.105 --> 00:22:34.566
-Weren't you. Floyd? Aww!
-[Floyd purring]

508
00:22:35.233 --> 00:22:38.695
Come back next time. and we'll open up
another Dollhouse Surprise.

509
00:22:39.654 --> 00:22:41.365
[as Hamster Kitty] Bye! [giggles]
